**Summary of the domain strategy brief:**

**Recommendation: Option D — Hybrid (keep freesoft.ru, consolidate rest on freesoft.net subdomains)**

- **freesoft.ru** (168K, DR 59) stays untouched — zero migration risk
- **frees0ft.fr** → **fr.freesoft.net** (fixes spelling issue, low risk: DR 23, 24 followed backlinks)
- New languages (es, ar, pt, id, vi) launch as **\*.freesoft.net** subdomains
